<html lang="ca">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <title>Email verificat</title>
    <style>
      body { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
      height: 100vh; background-color: #f8f9fa; } .card { width: 400px;
      background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; } .card-header img {
      width: 100%; height: auto; } .card-footer img { width: 216px; height:
      auto; margin: 0 auto; display: block; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <img src="https://365equipo.com/logo365Email.png" alt="365 Logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="card-text">
          Perfecte! L'email s'ha verificat correctament. T'hem enviat la teva
          identificació per QR al teu email, però si el prefereixes, pots
          afegir-lo directament a Wallet.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <a href="{{walletUrl}}">
          <img
            src="https://365equipo.com/ca_add_to_google_wallet_add-wallet-badge.svg"
            alt="Añadir a Wallet"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>